142
00:19:49,605 --> 00:19:51,005
Your shoulder, here.

143
00:19:52,341 --> 00:19:53,774
Your back, here.

144
00:19:54,777 --> 00:19:55,971
Your legs, here.

145
00:20:05,387 --> 00:20:09,653
