Put them on for now.

242
00:34:20,642 --> 00:34:22,842
I won't take advantage of you.

243
00:35:36,985 --> 00:35:38,495
Have you seen enough?

244
00:35:39,821 --> 00:35:41,741
Please hand me the clothes.

245
00:35:44,325 --> 00:35:45,825
You knew I was here?

246
00:35:46,661 --> 00:35:49,029
Master Wind wanders like the wind.

247
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:51,230
I'd expect you to be anywhere.

248
00:36:15,990 --> 00:36:18,550
You look different in men's clothes.

249
00:36:19,193 --> 00:36:20,403
Do I look awful?

250
00:36:28,536 --> 00:36:31,505
I will tell all the girls
to wear men's clothes

251
00:36:31,506 --> 00:36:35,169
