256
00:37:08,443 --> 00:37:10,883
You knew I was watching you bathe,

257
00:37:10,979 --> 00:37:12,879
yet you said nothing.

258
00:37:16,818 --> 00:37:19,082
You saved my life.

259
00:37:20,288 --> 00:37:22,347
You can look all you please.

260
00:38:44,906 --> 00:38:47,166
I thought you were hot as fire.

261
00:38:47,475 --> 00:38:49,675
In fact, you're cool as water.

262
00:38:53,114 --> 00:38:55,254
